[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    115[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **File:** `chapter13.10-python-example.md`
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    116[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Section:** Step 7, `local_query_adapter_handler` function
